title: COVID-19 Tests for Infection & Immunity | Quest®
description: Regardless of if you had symptoms or were asymptomatic, shop online for COVID-19 tests to check for active infections or immunity antibodies.
cleaned_text: Shop online for COVID-19 tests to check for active infections or immunity antibodies - even if you're asymptomatic. Once you purchase a test, it's easy to schedule an appointment at one of 2000+ Quest Diagnostics locations nationwide. You'll get fast results online and have the option to discuss them with an independent physician at no extra cost.
